                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17351888" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 15:39:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mck&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mck&quot;&gt;mck&lt;/a&gt; shouldn&apos;t we at least let a user with a source dist pull in the driver when they build with ant?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17351902" author="michaelsembwever" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 16:08:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m thinking we leave the python dependency in the source artefact.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the last board report we were told that the policy has been updated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It currently stands as&#8230;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SOURCE PACKAGES&lt;br/&gt;
Every ASF release MUST contain one or more source packages, which MUST be sufficient for a user to build and test the release provided they have access to the appropriate platform and tools. A source release SHOULD not contain compiled code.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Those python zip files are not compiled. And it only says &quot;SHOULD not&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17351913" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 16:20:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should we just ninja out the removal then?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17351933" author="michaelsembwever" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 16:55:12 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Should we just ninja out the removal then?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17351964" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 17:29:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The line removing the driver &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-4.0/build.xml#L1167&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-4.0/build.xml#L1167&lt;/a&gt; is also excluding the rest of lib, so this won&apos;t be a simple single line removal.  I&apos;ll post a patch shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17352022" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 26 May 2021 19:00:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not very complicated after all, so done in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/f4ab8cce1e4f517406c1343d369326916586db67&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/f4ab8cce1e4f517406c1343d369326916586db67&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
